messages.messageBody:
Although I had seen the image search option on google, I had never used it.

That was SO COOL!!! THANK YOU, Nancy!

After I got some lambs, I put in truck+pickup to see if I could find a pickup
better than the one I have at my leaning on a truck article.


There wasn't a better one, but there were some good ones I'll probably
incorporate!

I will have to force myself to quit playing with that at some point today. I
came here to say thanks, and I'm going back!

Sandra

Simple GIFs .. 'Tis a GIF that is simple, 'Tis a GIF that is free...


I thought that was cute.

I'm kind of brain-tired from looking through Christian art sites for a plain
little lying-down cheap-graphics lamb, for my theology (almost) webpage.

I'll find one. I used to have one.

But I liked the gif-parody.

I love the internet, but I love freeways and malls too, and they can be as
stress-inducing and irritating as all get-out.

Sandra
